Wow, what a year 2022 has been. Much of this year has been difficult for me, but as I look back on it through the pictures and videos in my camera roll I realize there’s been some really great times too.
•
As I mature, I’m finding that the freedom that comes from owning my business is what I like about it the most. Sure, I still love designing with flowers, helping couples create a magical day, and teaching other designers what I know to positively impact their businesses, but ultimately, I love spending time with my Bella Boo, my hubby, and our friends!
•
So, if you’ve had a hard year, take time to go through your camera roll and figure out what days made you smile and let’s figure out how to replicate those kind of moments in 2023!
